sion=\"1\" data-media-id=\"e35d3cbc-19c7-495a-bb8a-6047e702d29d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219348/LamaConductor_roughness.0005.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330547900&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=434&amp;height=434 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219348/LamaConductor_roughness.0005.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330547900&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=217&amp;height=217 1x\"></span><p style=\"text-align: center;\">0.8</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"LamaConductor_roughness.0006.jpg\" width=\"217\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219348/LamaConductor_roughness.0006.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330547900&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=217&amp;height=217\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219348/LamaConductor_roughness.0006.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330547900&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"800\" data-width=\"800\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219396\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"LamaConductor_roughness.0006.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219348\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"7aaa09fb-0eac-4ee4-9c5c-33cce9c6650b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219348/LamaConductor_roughness.0006.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330547900&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=434&amp;height=434 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219348/LamaConductor_roughness.0006.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330547900&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=217&amp;height=217 1x\"></span><p style=\"text-align: center;\">1.0</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><br/><strong>Normal/Bump</strong></p><p>Here is where you supply a signal, either a texture or procedural pattern, to create a bump to the surface to &quot;fake&quot; surface details like small bumps or scratches. This means an artist doesn't have to model these tedious and often repetitious parts of a model.<br/><br/></p><hr/><h3 id=\"LamaConductor-TailParameters\">Tail Parameters</h3><p><strong>Mix</strong></p><p>How strong the reflection tail effect is as a linear measurement 0 to 1, or maximum strength</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table data-table-width=\"1800\" data-layout=\"center\" data-local-id=\"adb15e88-afd6-4483-ba92-9943d34ffafe\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 113.33px;\"/><col style=\"width: 113.33px;\"/><col style=\"width: 113.33px;\"/><col style=\"width: 113.33px;\"/><col style=\"width: 113.33px;\"/><col style=\"width: 113.33px;\"/></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"6\" class=\"confluenceTh\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Mix examples:</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"LamaConductor_tailmix.0001.jpg\" width=\"217\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219348/LamaConductor_tailmix.0001.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330547708&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=217&amp;height=217\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219348/LamaConductor_tailmix.0001.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330547708&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"800\" data-width=\"800\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219393\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"LamaConductor_tailmix.0001.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219348\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ff1ed924-56f5-4610-a78b-2b5f74308171\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219348/LamaConductor_tailmix.0001.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330547708&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=434&amp;height=434 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219348/LamaConductor_tailmix.0001.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330547708&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=217&amp;height=217 1x\"></span><p style=\"text-align: center;\">0.0</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"LamaConductor_tailmix.0002.jpg\" width=\"217\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219348/LamaConductor_tailmix.0002.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330547708&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=217&amp;height=217\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219348/LamaConductor_tailmix.0002.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330547708&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"800\" data-width=\"800\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219390\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"LamaConductor_tailmix.0002.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-lin